  "title": "Service Crew / Supervisor (Full Time / Part Time)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p><p>You will be responsible for greeting, preparing and serving food and beverages, delivering excellent customer service. You will also maintain a clean, organized restaurant and ensuring compliance with all safety and legal regulations at all times.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Greet guests, take orders, delivering excellent customer service</li><li>Process guests orders into the Point-of-Sale (POS) system</li><li>Knowledgeable of food and beverages menus, promote ongoing menu offerings</li><li>Prepare and serve alcoholic and non-alcoholic beverages and food</li><li>Anticipate guests' needs, respond promptly to any requests or concerns to ensure their satisfaction</li><li>Engaging with guests throughout the dining experience</li><li>Daily housekeeping tasks to ensure cleanliness and organization of the work environment</li><li>Ensure all equipment is in good working condition</li><li>Monitor and manage inventory levels of alcoholic and non-alcoholic supplies</li><li>Perform and support daily restaurant operations</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Basic Safety & Hygiene Certification</li><li>Customer focused</li><li>Operate point-of-sale (POS) accurately and efficiently</li><li>Able to work on weekends and public holidays</li><li>Opening and closing restaurant operations</li><li>Teamwork </li><li>Full Time / Part Time</li></ul>",
